{"word":"G1966 - ἐπιοῦσα - epioûsa - ep-ee-oo'-sah - Following","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιοῦσα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epioûsa</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ee-oo'-sah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Following</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"தொடர்கிற, மறுநாள் - இடைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"the next day"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine singular participle of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0314;&#x0342;&#x03BC;&#x03B9;</b> <b>heimi</b> (to <i>go</i>); <i>supervening</i>, that is, (<a href=\"#/G2250 - ἡμέρα - hēméra - hay-mer'-ah/2250\">G2250</a> or <a href=\"#/G3571 - νύξ - nýx - noox/3571\">G3571</a> being expressed or implied) the <i>ensuing</i> day or night: - following, next.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}